{"pageProps":{"post":{"title":"package.json이 뭔데?!","date":"2023-02-14","slug":"2023-02-14-package.json","content":"<h1>📦 package.json의 역할</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><code>package.json</code>은 프로젝트의 정보와 패키지 버전을 관리하는 파일</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>package.json</p>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"name\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"프로젝트 이름\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"version\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"0.1.0\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">// 프로젝트 버전</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"private\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">true</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"scripts\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: {</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">...</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">},</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"dependencies\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: {</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">...</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">},</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"devDependencies\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: {</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">...</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h1>📦 package.json 생성 및 구성요소</h1>\n<h2>package.json 만들기</h2>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">$</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">npm</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">init</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">     </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">//</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">프로젝트명,</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">설명</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">등</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">작성할</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">내용이</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">있을</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">경우</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">$</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">npm</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">init</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">-y</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">//</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">입력할</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">내용없이</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">package.json</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">생성</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>package.json</p>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"name\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"temp\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"version\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"1.0.0\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"description\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"main\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"index.js\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"scripts\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"test\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"echo </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">\\\"</span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">Error: no test specified</span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">\\\"</span><span style=\"color: #98C379\"> &#x26;&#x26; exit 1\"</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  },</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"keywords\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: [],</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"author\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"license\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"ISC\"</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<h2>구성요소</h2>\n<p>package.json에 있는 field 요소 설명!</p>\n<p>참고로 ⭐은 필수로 없으면 설치가 불가능하다</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>⭐<strong>name</strong>: 패키지의 이름</p>\n<ul>\n<li>소문자로만 작성</li>\n<li>한 단어로 작성</li>\n<li><code>-</code>(하이픈)이나 <code>_</code>(언더스코어)를 포함 가능</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>⭐<strong>version</strong>: 설치된 패키지의 버전</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>description</strong>: 패키지 설명</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>main</strong>: 패키지의 메인 파일</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>scripts</strong>: 자주 실행하는 반복 명령어\r\n<a href=\"https://www.notion.so/Scripts-d7bee9cabf0b4b0ea032d781f983d618\">Scripts 더 자세히 보기</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>keywords</strong>: 패키지 키워드</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>author, contributors</strong>: 패키지 제작자 / author(한명), contributors(여러명)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>license:</strong> 패키지의 권한</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>bugs</strong>: 패키지의 이슈와 버그트래킹을 볼 수 있는 url과 이슈를 알릴 email 주소 입력</p>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"bugs\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"url\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"https://github.com/name/project/issues\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"email\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"temp@naver.com\"</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  }</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>homepage</strong>: 패키지의 홈페이지 경로가 있는 경우 기입</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>repository</strong>: 소스 코드가 관리되는 저장소 위치</p>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"repository\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"type\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"git\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"url\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"https://github.com/name/project.git\"</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  }</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>type</strong>: 패키지 모든 파일에 node.js가 사용하는 모듈 형식 정의\r\n만약 선언되지 않을 경우 기본 <code>Commonjs</code> 사용\r\n<strong>module은 esm 지원</strong></p>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"type\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"module\"</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>exports:</strong> <a href=\"https://toss.tech/article/commonjs-esm-exports-field\">글</a> 참고</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>engines:</strong> 동작 가능한 node, npm 버전 지정</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>dependencies</strong>: 애플리케이션 동작과 연관된 라이브러리</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>devDependencies</strong>: 애플리케이션 동작과 직접적 연관은 없지만 개발에 필요한 라이브러리</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h1>📦 package.json의 모듈 버전</h1>\n<p>package.json의 모듈 버전은 Semenantic Versioning(SemVer)을 따름</p>\n<div class=\"alert\">\r\n  <h6>SemVer이란?</h6>\r\n  <p>0.0.0 처럼 세 자리 숫자로 버전을 명시하는 방법으로, [major, minor, patch] 순으로 작성</p>\r\n</div>\n<h3>Major (<span class=\"point\">0</span>.0.0)</h3>\n<p>첫 번째 자리: <strong><em>정식 버전과 하위 호환이 불가능한 기능 변경</em></strong>을 의미</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>0</code> 으로 시작인 경우 정식 출시 전 초기 개발단계 (ex. “gulp”: “0.1.0”)</li>\n<li><code>1</code> 이상 이면 정식 버전을 의미 (ex. “gulp”: “1.1.0”)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Minor (0.<span class=\"point\">0</span>.0)</h3>\n<p>두 번째 자리:<strong><em>하위 호환이 가능한 기능 변경</em></strong>을 의미</p>\n<h3>Patch (0.0.<span class=\"point\">0</span>)</h3>\n<p>세 번째 자리: 기능의 추가보다는 <strong><em>버그가 수정된 경우</em></strong> 숫자를 올림</p>\n<br>\n<h2>다양한 버전 표시 방법</h2>\n<p>package.json의 버전을 보면 아래와 같이 기호들이 작성되어있는데, 이는 버전의 정보를 표시하는 방식이다</p>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"dependencies\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"a\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"1.2.3\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"b\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\">1.2.3\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"c\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\">=1.2.3\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"d\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"&#x3C;1.2.3\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"e\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"&#x3C;=1.2.3\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"f\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"^1.2.3\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">\"g\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">: </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">\"~1.2.3\"</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>>, >=, &#x3C;, &#x3C;=</h3>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1.2</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">3</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">>= </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1.2</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">3</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&#x3C; </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1.2</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">3</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&#x3C;= </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1.2</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">3</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>지정한 버전보다 <strong>초과, 이상, 미만, 이하</strong>인 버전으로 업데이트 가능</li>\n<li><code>≤ 1.2.3</code>은 1.2.3, 1.1.8로 업데이트 가능 / 1.2.4, 1.4.0 업데이트 불가능</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>*<strong>*x**</strong></h3>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1.2</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.x</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><code>x</code>로 표시된 버전만 자동 업데이트가 가능</li>\n<li><code>1.2.x</code>는 1.2.3로 업데이트가 가능 / 1.3.0으로 업데이트 불가능</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>*<strong>*Tilde(틸드, ~)**</strong></h3>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">~</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1.2</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">3</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> : </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1.2</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">3</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> &#x3C;= version &#x3C; </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1.3</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">0</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> (patch 버전업 가능)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">~</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1.2</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">   : </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1.2</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">0</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> &#x3C;= version &#x3C; </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1.3</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">0</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> (patch 버전업 가능 / </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1.2</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.x와 동일)ㅗㄱ</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><code>minor</code> 버전이 명시되었다는 가정 하에 <strong><code>patch</code> 버전을 자동 업데이트</strong></li>\n<li><code>minor</code> 버전이 명시되지 않은 경우, <code>minor</code> 버전 업이 허용</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>*<strong>*Caret(캐럿, ^)**</strong></h3>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"json\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">^</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1.2</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">3</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> : </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1.2</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">3</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> &#x3C;= version &#x3C; </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">2.0</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">^</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1.2</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">   : </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1.2</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">0</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> &#x3C;= version &#x3C; </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">2.0</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">^</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">     : </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1.0</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">0</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> &#x3C;= version &#x3C; </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">2.0</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>기본적으로 <code>**minor</code>, <code>patch</code> 버전을 자동으로 업데이트**</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h1>📦 마무리</h1>\n<p>package.json의 기호와 field에 대해 알게 되었는데,<br>\n추후 기존 프로젝트나 새 프로젝트를 이해하는데 도움이 될지 않을까…? 생각이 듭니다…ㅎㅎ… 😼</p>\n<hr>\n<h1>📦 부록</h1>\n<p><a href=\"/assets/blog/posts/2023-02-14-dependencies\"><strong>dependencies</strong> vs. <strong>devDependencies</strong></a></p>"}},"__N_SSG":true}